  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink39-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">oru ñāṉṟu talaivaṉ taṉ maṉaikkaṇ ceṉṟatu koṇṭu avaṉ peṇmai nalamellām
          tuyttuk kātal nīṅkip pirintāṉ eṉpatu talaivi kūṟiṉāḷ eṉak kēṭṭa parattai avaṭkup
          pāṅkāyiṉār kēṭpat taṉ tōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink39">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi yūraṉ</l>
          <l> vemmulai yaṭaiya muyaṅki namvayiṟ</l>
          <l> ṟiruntiḻai paṇaittōṇ ñekiḻap</l>
          <l> pirintaṉa ṉāyiṉum piriyalaṉ maṉṉē</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l> Alas, [my] friend! </l>
          <l>Although he left–  </l> 
            <l>the man from the village</l>
          <l>after tightly embracing [our] hot breasts</l>
          <l>so that our perfect, bejewelled, bamboo-like shoulders grew emaciated</l>
          <l> –he didn't really leave.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
